Global Grease Removal Equipment Market Insights
Grease Removal Equipment Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Grease Removal Equipment Market Overview
The grease removal equipment market is witnessing significant growth, driven by increasing demand across various industries including food processing, automotive, and wastewater management. As businesses focus on improving operational efficiency and reducing environmental impact, grease removal solutions have become essential. The market was valued at USD 4.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2025 to 2030, reaching USD 7.6 billion by 2030. This growth is attributed to the rising need for cleaner and more sustainable operations in both industrial and commercial sectors. Furthermore, increasing environmental regulations across regions are spurring the adoption of grease removal technologies. The market includes various equipment types such as grease traps, interceptors, and filtration systems, all playing a crucial role in effective grease management systems across multiple applications.

